Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-a)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请D区150号之前的观众入场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易混乱受伤 所以请排队入场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.29,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs42\shad0\c&H565959&\pos(374,222)}羽佐间正义先生的公寓发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.29,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs42\shad0\c&H565959&\pos(376,272)}原因是天然气泄露？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉明戈小哥还真是不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人伤脑筋呢 这样会损害麻里的形象的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为羽佐间先生在麻里拯救世界的时候出了一份力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的心目中已经被篡改成那样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「部下的过失是领队的责任」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果别人这么说了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是弗拉明戈少女团还是弗拉明戈现在都停业中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且事到如今也不会有人来抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生？那算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 大家都被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的大家也包括那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说后藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生这事先暂且不提 那边你也好好做个了断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么了断？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样下去你甘心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要问你 这样下去你甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一起努力办好演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM 东京巨蛋 Live and Peace！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Live and Peace！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车 快叫救护车！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,告訴我什麼是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为服用了有毒的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚为她们做了洗胃 现在需要观察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要调查过成分才能下结论 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在举办演唱会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM的三泽瑞希和森田萌小姐在公演中突然倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在开演前喝下了含有药物的咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻里 现在无法接听您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在哔声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 回个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的目的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只有我消失才能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我令他变成那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个方法可以承担责任……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领队！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚刚醒了 可以进去探望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非比常人的恢复力 不愧是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说想先和你单独见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 我们等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容整形应该去其他医院才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害您变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然犯人是跟你有关的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「替我向弗拉明戈武士先生问好」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的红斧之耳拥有常人7倍的听力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实听到了你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他了吧 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的红斧之眼拥有常人12倍的视…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽田灰司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做泽田灰司 是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的文具不卖给警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些可以用来镇压暴徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上已经没有暴徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿川 之前的事你考虑过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养子的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得不太合适…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘 说到养子应该先找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小苍太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H53B55B&\shad0\bord0\fs60}离 婚 申 请 书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽田灰司…这次出现了一个棘手的敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就像是在和幽灵战斗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在记录上已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却接二连三地袭击我身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果英雄陷入了危机 该向谁求助呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会寻求他人帮助的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么痛苦 无论遭遇多么不讲理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须自己承受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独才是我们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛酸吧 很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 人类才时而会被邪恶所诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也正因如此 我们才握有绝对无敌的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来 你还没有掌握它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父 请别说笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是在说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是无穷无限的最强之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让人变得无比强大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爱能成为正义的伙伴 那就什么都不必害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掌握爱吧 羽佐间正义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂…我不懂啊 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爱会使人变强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 要怎么做才能掌握爱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这需要你自己领悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父！请别敷衍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我真没办法教你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爱的形式和掌握它的要领都因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能告诉你的只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 你们进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 看起来很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}要先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}小姐 肛门科不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我的肛门可是很健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Part-B)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz358.813\pos(612,548)\c&H363636&}小后。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz356.32\pos(536,578)\c&H363636&}这样下去真的好吗？(>_<)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz355.285\pos(506,610)\c&H363636&}你真的不再见正义了吗？(T_T)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤 现在可是上班时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去挨家挨户巡逻一下 这里就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 妈妈抱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 我的脑子里都只有英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道…什么是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0700,0000,,正义 正义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0700,0000,0000,,爱…爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你从刚刚开始就不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么烦恼 就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得和你谈也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 可以暂时别理我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机先生 我要更改目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 这个 这个 这个 还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一次上的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是发给出版商的简历
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加综艺节目时的台本 当时的收视率表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,访谈 海报和日历
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这是你出道时的第一张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容也很僵硬 比外行人还糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你也有自己的闪光点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始就很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有他人所没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个值得我赌一把的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都更早注视你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人我可是看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 弗拉明戈武士的事我一开始就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睁只眼闭只眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果你就瞪鼻子上脸 从弗拉明戈变成了Flamenger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉明戈星人算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的设计全都打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和原定计划偏了十万八千里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我今后也想继续关注你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你有烦恼 就请告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为都烧光了 原来这个还留着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了石原小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子不是死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他确实出现在我的周围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父也说看到了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得他并不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 还是第一次接到你主动打来的电话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 而且我觉得这应该也是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请你帮我查一下一位名叫泽田灰司的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽田灰司？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察说他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你觉得警察都不知道的事情我会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然觉得你又讨厌又烦人又难对付又让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你那可疑的情报网和行动力还是最让人信赖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是至今为止最让我高兴的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我这就查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐 你好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是爱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没喜欢过女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止一次都没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 因为我一直忙于英雄的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐 爱是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很棒的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再详细点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法代替的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具体点！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没法说具体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱有很多种形式 没法说清道明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父也是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他说只能自己掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在小时候都是由父母抚养的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说你是爷爷抚养的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爷爷想保护你的心情 这就是爱的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母相遇 想要共度人生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一种爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的粉丝们为你加油打气 这也是一种爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上充满了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有注意到的人就体会不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为 爱发生在不同人的身上 能轻易地变成其他的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成其他感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对英雄的感情 这也一定是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽田对你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根到底也许也是一种爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是比喻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于不懂得爱的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会拘泥 执着 时而愤怒或是憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要照顾你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某种意义上说或许也是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是从某种意义上说啊 某种意义上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱虽然很美好 但同时也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才会为此饱受折磨 却仍然不懈追求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有爱也无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了啊 你或许只是没有发觉自己内心的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我内心的爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我找不到手机了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这才是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这也不是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}收到了「她」的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.71,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(516,506)\c&H4C4C4C&}小后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.71,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(508,544)\c&H4C4C4C&}还好吗～？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.71,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(500,580)\c&H4C4C4C&}我很好哦～。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.71,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(490,620)\c&H4C4C4C&}骗你的骗你的。
